review:
I have been visiting Dr Narayan babu for last 6 years since 2018 and am extremely satisfied with all the services from Root Canal to filling to tooth extraction to cleaning and polishing. 

I would recommend everyone to go to him for any tooth related problem and you will be highly satisfied.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Wait time,
review:
This was my first experience with Dr. Narayan Babu.
The first experience I got was his patience and comforting talks made me relax and removed my anxiety.
Second thing is his  confidence building talks about the problem for which I went to him.
Third thing is his suggestion to me what remedial measures can be taken if the problem repeats.
Final point is the atmosphere and cleanliness of the treatment room.
All qualities of a experiences doctor was seen in him.
May the Lord Jesus bless him and prosper him to bless many more who come to him.

tags: Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,
review: I had undergone orthodontic treatment five years back.. The teeth got relapsed and the gaps between teeth started to develop and became visibly obvious. I had my marriage in 6 months and wanted to get it corrected asap. Dr.Narayan Babu suggested me the best treatment where in he suggested me to go for orthodontic treatment again to close all the visible gaps in upper jaw and he even did cosmetic correction to make it aesthetically look better. Within 6 months I had the best and most confident smile and I thank doctor for making the entire experience so professional and flawless. I forever cherish the pics of my marriage with such a bright smile.. :) Also, the gaps between teeth of lower jaw was also corrected post marriage and now I have no gaps and shining with perfect smile..:)
